## 5. Mental Model
- Organization: The top-level Property Management Company. It owns the entire portfolio.
- Folders: Regional groupings. For example, dividing the portfolio into "Wales Properties" and "Scotland Properties"
  (sub folders "areas in wales" & "areas in Scotland") 
- Projects The inividual rental house, what happnes to a house in scotland doesn't effect the house in wales
- Resources, whats inside the houes boiler sofa fridge ect 

- IAM The keys to the house (who has access Tennant Living there, plumber there just to fix the boiler) and the tennancy aggrement (what they can do inside the property)

- Billing the Gas, eletrice & water attached to the house
- Networking The priveate roads connecting the properties 

If you demolish a house (a Project), all the appliances inside are destroyed, and the utility meter stops billing immediately.
